Implement this exercise.

**Answer:**

```cpp
std::optional<T> peek() const {
    std::lock_guard<std::mutex> lock(mutex_);

    if (queue_.empty()) {
        return std::nullopt;
    }

    return queue_.front();  // Copy
}
