Implement this exercise.

**Answer:**

```cpp
R operator()(Args... args) {
    if (!callable_) {
        throw std::bad_function_call();
    }

    try {
        return callable_->invoke(std::forward<Args>(args)...);
    } catch (...) {
        // Re-wrap exception
        throw std::runtime_error("Exception in std::function invocation");
    }
}
```

